## 2. Gameplay Rules

Exotic Car DeX is designed to provide fair and enjoyable gameplay for all users.

Users must not:

* Abuse, exploit, or manipulate bot mechanics
* Use automated tools, scripts, selfbots, or external programs to gain an unfair advantage
* Exploit bugs or glitches instead of reporting them
